Cure Critical Wounds
Discworld ritual help
Cure Critical Wounds

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Cure critical wounds -- Heals all but the most critical of wounds.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Cure critical wounds can be performed on a person or on yourself.  It gives
back a large number of hit points.  You need a holy symbol to
perform this ritual and, the success is based on your
faith.rituals.curing skill.
.EP